com.martinandersson.javaee.jpa.entitymanagers.lib

Class Products

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.martinandersson.javaee.jpa.entitymanagers.lib.Products

  • public final class Products
extends Object
    Utility class with functional factory methods for all CRUD-like operations expected from a Product repository.

    The produced functions are normally used as arguments to a EntityManagerExposer.

    Author:
    Martin Andersson (webmaster at martinandersson.com)
